{"word":"H8154 - שָׁסָה - shâçâh - shaw-saw' - Destroyer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁסָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâçâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-saw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Destroyer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொள்ளையாடு, கொள்ளை, வாரிக்கொண்டுபோ, கொள்ளைக்காரன்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to spoil, to plunder, to take spoil"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to plunder"},{"paragraph":"2) plunderers (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Poel) to plunder"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (The second form being used in Isa 10:13); a primitive root; to <i>plunder: - </i>destroyer, rob, spoil (-er)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}